reviews: This unit is made of very thin neoprene, like the dollar store quality one I never use. It will not protect your glasses when hanging. It is fine for a purse or a bag, but not for hanging free. It is just a fabric case. I will not risk $1500 prescription glasses hanging in this floppy cloth case.This item would be great if it was just made exactly the same but with thicker fabric. As it is unusable as a hanging case, I give it a 1 star. I would have given it 0 stars if I could because it is going in the garbage. Everyone should now to be aware before buying, it's literally "dollarama" quality.

review_title: Protection from scratching but limited colors & designs.
reviews: I bought these (bought 2) to leave in the car and protect my sunglasses from getting scratched. They will do exactly that. If you are looking to protect your glasses from being sat on these are not for you. The zipper seems fairly durable (plastic) and smooth operating. The clip (also plastic) is surprisingly stronger than it looks. The inside is soft but won't leave lint balls all over your glasses. The only thing that I was a little disappointed in was the limited color or designs. All in all they do the job they were meant to do.
